","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2965ef24b98ce189d5e6d205e1829154","url_token":"kun-shao-93-29","name":"坤少","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e9d24f2ee208a7ad32f3e197bbe8545a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e9d24f2ee208a7ad32f3e197bbe8545a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2965ef24b98ce189d5e6d205e1829154","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563947994","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-37dccdbf63a94903fb0ee5ae2a0c3b30_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546314223,"updated_time":1546314223,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e从你的问题来看呢，你是想通过证明哥德巴赫猜想来上清华。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先你要清楚的明白自己的目的是上清华，但是上清华最直接简单的方式难道不是通过高考吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然不知道你为何直接否定这种方式，但是高考是很明确的并且绝对能实现的方式。是你对自己的高考不自信吗？那你现在更应该去看看自己哪一点没掌握好，然后弥补那个缺口尽可能地通过高考来达到自己的目标。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e至于你的方式，我很钦佩你能有这样的想法，也很期待你能实践自己的想法，或许你就是数学界的一颗新星呢？固然这条路会有很多困难，若你感觉自己有希望，请别放弃，至少不要自己后悔吧。但是我还是想提醒你一句尽力而为，认清自己的条件，做出正确的判断以达到最理想的程度。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2b12ae589a4521d01ecade51b666c27c_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"700\" data-rawheight=\"945\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1ac3f5ed23c817c1361e57dca31f7f38_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"700\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2b12ae589a4521d01ecade51b666c27c_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='700'%20height='945'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-